        <li><span class="font-medium">Drag health:</span> request a quick drag smoothness check after service.</li>
        <li><span class="font-medium">Brand support:</span> confirm parts for your reel (Shimano, Daiwa, Penn, Abu, etc.).</li>
        <li><span class="font-medium">Turnaround:</span> spooling is usually same-day; deeper repairs take longer.</li>
